msgSnippet: But in this case, two wrongs do in fact make a right. ... That s really hard to think about. And they could both be wrong ... ... confidential, proprietary or
messageBody:
But in this case, two wrongs do in fact make a right.

-----Original Message-----

> How about

> assertEquals(a.equals(b), b.equals(a));

> which makes the test obviously about symmetry.

That's really hard to think about. And they could both be wrong ...
